      "full_name": "Juhang Aviation Technology Shenzhen Co. Limited",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Juhang Aviation Technology Shenzhen Co. Limited (Juhang Aviation) is a Chinese company involved in a procurement and manufacturing network for the Russian military-industrial complex. Through a Russian intermediary, OOO TSK Vektor, Juhang Aviation has delivered components to IEMZ Kupol, a subsidiary of Russian state-owned arms company Almaz-Antey, which subsequently were used for manufacturing long-range attack drones of the type Garpiya-3 (G3) for use in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. This also includes components from Xiamen Limbach, a Chinese entity producing L550 drone engines.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}